##The coroner, Liu Liang, detailed the autopsy and is expected to draw a conclusion within 10 days

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

This is a roundup for the paper

February 16, Wuhan. Two autopsies of the newly deceased were carried out at the Golden Pool Hospital under legal policy, and the pathology of the new pneumonia obtained from the autopsies has now been examined.

Journalist, Zhu Wenbo, editor, Zhang Zhaoyi, video source, relevant Person Responsible Editor: Zhou Kuanwei

According to Liu Liang, a forensic pathologist and president of the Hubei Forensic Association, who was involved in the autopsy, he worked with team members and other experts to dissect the bodies of both victims, each taking nearly three hours, the autopsy pathology has been sent to the lab, and the results are expected within 10 days.

On February 16th, at 2312 hours, Liu Liang posted on her headline account, Liu Liang, a medical examiner, a detailed autopsy of two cases of new pneumonia in 18 hours, going through Florida

At about 2100 hours on February 15, Liu Liang suddenly received a call from the head of the hospital, Zhang Dingyu, saying that there was a body of a deceased patient with new pneumonia who could be dissected.

Liu Liang rushed the team to the hospital and waited until after 1 a.m. for the autopsy to begin.

Liu Liang, left, wearing a protective suit

Within 10 minutes of wearing the suit for the first time, Liu Liang was sweating profusely, breathing hard, and his glasses and goggles were hazy. Halfway through the surgery, he developed hypoglycemia, panic attacks, dizziness.

At 0350 hours, the autopsy was completed.

After two hours of sleep at home, Liu Liang woke up and worked with the team to identify areas of improvement and logistical problems in the autopsy process and report back to the person in charge.

Liu Liang (center) poses with team members

At about 11:00 on February 16, Liu Liang received another call from Zhang Dingyu, the body of a new case of pneumonia to autopsy.

Liu Liang again called for emergency personnel, to the Golden Pool Hospital, 16:00 pm Autopsy, 18:30 end.

Liu Liang believes that the autopsy was carried out so quickly thanks to the consent of the family, as well as the efficient emergency meeting of the National Health Commission, which is basically an ad hoc model. While the documents were issued urgently, give verbal notification to the key hospitals immediately.

On February 15, the medical and Health Administration Bureau of the National Health Commission convened a meeting in Wuhan to study issues related to autopsies of new cases of pneumonia, and invited Liu Liang as an expert to attend the meeting.

They observed a moment of silence before the Feb. 16 autopsy, Liu Liang said.

It is known that the pathology of new coronary pneumonia obtained by dissection has been examined, and it is expected to find the pathogenicity and fatal pathology of new coronary pneumonia, and to provide evidence for the future clinical treatment of critically ill patients.

(comprehensive Legal Daily, China News Service)
